{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset contains 22,660,003 linkages between 3,017,441 patents and 4,017,152 papers.",
    "We merged the Reliance on Science dataset with Dimensions using the DOI (Digital Object Identifier-a unique, universal identifier).",
    "This procedure matched all 4,017,152 papers in the Reliance on Science dataset to those in our Dimensions subsample.",
    "Next, we use data from the United States Patent and Trademark Office (USPTO).",
    "We collect assignee information and renewal status for each patent citing a paper."
  ]
}